Teltoli eeped as the air was knocked from her lungs, and the back of 
her head slammed into WindLord's chest. Quickly, she rolled off him 
and looked up as two bots came to cover them. Teltoli smiled, and 
reached into her wrist container, which held some healing herbs.

She held them to WindLord's back wound, and the mechfluid stopped 
flowing and it healed, amazingly, till it was only an inch big. The 
herbs were absorbed in the Hawk's armour. She smiled and leaned back, 
wincing.

"For the future, big bot, my name's Teltoli SilverWing" She smiled, 
and stood up painfully, grabbing the gun she had held earlier and 
watching the sky.
